# Secrets — never commit, regardless of which subproject they're in
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Dependencies / build output
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.venv/
**/venv/

# Local data / vector stores
**/chroma-data/
**/chroma_db/

# Claude Code local-only settings
**/.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Misc
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
**/playwright-report/
**/test-results/
**/tta-report/
